      "body": "{\"flightCategoryList\":[{\"code\":\"1-1Q8B3OH3\",\"name\":\"Praia\",\"content\":{\"Cover_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/842226a3-c93a-4dc0-a4b8-86ca9ae7c633?size=150x310&type=jpg\",\"Description\":\"<p>A verdadeira viagem de descobrimento năo consiste em procurar novas paisagens e sim ter novos olhos<br><ins>Marcel Proust</ins></p>\\n\",\"Desktop_Background_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/bad1b7b3-ba7a-496b-bc7e-1805ed2bd012?size=1360x650&type=jpg\",\"Mobile_Background_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/9b97953a-f976-4833-b3af-f0a9ca5c67dc?size=340x744&type=jpg\",\"Is_Spotlight\":\"1\"}},{\"code\":\"1-1Q8B3OH1\",\"name\":\"Frio\",\"content\":{\"Cover_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/a3662713-bb6c-4106-876d-06d976d8421d?size=316x150&type=png\",\"Description\":\"<p>Em algum lugar alguma coisa incrível está esperando para ser conhecida<br><ins>Carl Sagan</ins></p>\\n\",\"Desktop_Background_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/65fad3c9-3edc-40a2-9735-986b47228b29?size=1360x650&type=jpg\",\"Mobile_Background_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/a8567e58-6400-402e-9759-81751a412dde?size=340x744&type=jpg\"}},{\"code\":\"1-1Q8B3OH2\",\"name\":\"História\",\"content\":{\"Cover_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/b9bc88d8-eb15-4180-ad8f-7442356e75ee?size=150x150&type=jpg\",\"Description\":\"<p>As pessoas năo fazem as viagens. As viagens é que fazem as pessoas<br><ins>John Steinbeck</ins></p>\\n\",\"Desktop_Background_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/bb5cd01d-6259-4f10-b302-da8eb0d407a1?size=1360x650&type=jpg\",\"Mobile_Background_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/d2948a56-c750-4c16-a536-5a121be9b8c8?size=340x744&type=jpg\"}},{\"code\":\"1-1Q8B3OH4\",\"name\":\"Natureza\",\"content\":{\"Cover_Image\":\"https://media-cms-prd.smiles.com.br/23c146f3-39e3-4442-a487-b0824ad2d2c4?size=150x150&type=jpg\",\"Description\":\"<p>Vá até onde puder ver. Quando chegar, p